        The Winter Months Between Octobers To April Are Considered To Be The Best Time To Visit Assam For Trekking As The Weather Is Cool, Dry And Pleasant. It Allows You Perfect Opportunity To Enjoy All That It Has To Offer Without Any Disruptions.    </p>
    <p>
       <b>Things To Carry</b><br/>
        Some Of The Important Things To Carry While Going For Trekking Includes The Basic Trek Gear Like Sleeping Bags, Mats, Proper Trekking Shoes, Adequate Clothing, Torch, Watch, Mobiles, Swiss Knives, Enough Food That Is Healthy And Nutritious, Camera Or Handy Cam Kit, Toiletry, Medicines Etc.
    </p>
    <p>
        <b>Precautions</b><br />
    As Much As It Is Fun, Trekking Can Also Be Quite Demanding. There Are Certain Precautions That One Needs To Take While Trekking. Ensure That You Don’t Carry Wanted Luggage And Make Sure That All Your Bags Are Waterproof. Get A Proper Medical Check-Up Done Before You Start And Ensure That You Have All That You Require. Do Not Overstress Yourself And If At Any Point Of Time You Feel Uncomfortable Seek Help Immediately.

</p>
    

